Crawley-based Acro Aircraft Seating recently unveiled the design for its new premium economy seat . 
  The ‘Series 7’ seat has hand-stitched leather armrests, aluminium chassis and composite materials . 
  Thompson Aero Seating has created a ‘Cozy Suite’ with dedicated sleeping positions . 
  Hong Kong’s Paperclip Design has a dual-decker armrest for long-haul flights . 
  The 'Meerkat Seat’ concept has a footrest and reclining backrest . 
 